---
title: Japanese Pork Tacos & Pickled Onion with Crispy Shallots
description: Tender pork strips get an aromatic boost in these speedy tacos inspired by Japanese flavours. With a crisp slaw, creamy aioli and lightly pickled onion to bring it all together, these are a fusion of some of the tastiest flavours around!
